        {
            "title": "吉利汽車7月份汽車總銷量按年增58%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">吉利汽車(00175)公布，7月份集團汽車總銷量23.77萬部，按年增長約58%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250317_FI_source-web_00175-3-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250317_FI_source-web_00175-3-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：吉利汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其中吉利品牌銷量19.35萬部，按年增70%；極氪銷量1.7萬部，較去年同期增8%；領克銷量2.72萬部，按年升28%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年首7個月合計，吉利集團總銷量累計達164.69萬部，較去年同期提升49%。其中吉利品牌銷量135.78萬部，按年升59%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15140843-%e5%90%89%e5%88%a9%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a7%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e7%b8%bd%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e58",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_00175-1.jpg.webp",
