        },
        {
            "title": "理想汽車上月交付新車按年降39.74%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015)公布，7月份交付近車3.07萬輛，較去年同期的5.1萬輛減少39.74%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250717_FI_source-web_02015-i8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250717_FI_source-web_02015-i8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：理想汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至7月底，該公司歷史累計交付量為136.85萬輛。該公司又指出，已於7月29日正式發佈家庭六坐純電SUV理想i8，計畫於8月20日開啟交付。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車截至7月底在全國已有535家零售中心，覆蓋153個城市；售後維修中心及授權鈑噴中心527家，覆蓋222個城市。理想汽車在全國已投入使用3028座理想超充站，擁有1.67萬個充電樁。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15140624-%e7%90%86%e6%83%b3%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e4%ba%a4%e4%bb%98%e6%96%b0%e8%bb%8a%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d39-74",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250331_FI_source-web_2015-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-01 16:40:26",
