            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱恒指跌265點報24507點 四連跌累挫1054點 騰訊與保險股領跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今日以跌市迎來8月份開局，並且連跌4日，累計跌逾千點；騰訊(00700)與保險股均是今日拖低大市的主力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Tencent_Group-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Tencent_Group-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開28點後，於早市原尚能呈好淡爭持，半日由最多升83點到最低時跌80點，可惜午後形勢轉壞，徘徊區下移至20天線(最新約為24757點)之下，大致於24500點至24700點上落，尾市最低曾見24507點，跌265點；恒指收報24507點，跌265點或1.07%，四連跌累計回吐1054點或4.12%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數今日則跌55點或1.02%，報5397點；國企指數跌78點或0.88%，報8804點。主板成交縮減至2546.74億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15140546-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c265%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124507%e9%bb%9e-%e5%9b%9b%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%af%e6%8c%ab1054%e9%bb%9e-%e9%a8%b0%e8%a8%8a%e8%88%87",
