            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "午後探底 滬指收跌13點 深指跌0.17% 芯片股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後再次探底，滬市壓力相對較重，油股固然持續弱勢，芯片股亦拾級向下，東芯股份(600110.SH)錄雙位數跌幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開4點後，於早市呈好淡爭持局面，半日由最多升8點到最低跌9點，高低位相差只得17點，午後壓力漸增，午市初段最跌至3550點，挫23點，其後才稍為回順；滬指收報3559點，跌13點或0.37%，成交6846.45億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指則由早市大部份時間報升，變為午市全程報跌，跌幅一度擴大至89點，報10919點，其後逐步收復失地，而全日高低位相差亦只有148點；深指最後收報10991點，跌18點或0.17%，成交9137.05億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌20點或0.51%，以4054點收市；創業板指數跌5點或0.24%，報2322點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寒武紀官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_688256-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寒武紀官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_688256-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寒武紀官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股受壓，東芯股份收市時跌11.37%，成交達61.56億元；AI芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)也跌2.88%。華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)跌2.25%，報58.67元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)跌1.35%，報88.29元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中石化(00386)昨天收市後發盈警，今日A、H齊跌，H股最多跌逾5.8%，中石化A股(600028.SH)也收跌5.32%，報5.69元，成交23.52億元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國石化微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石化.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國石化微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石化.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國石化微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">石油行業板塊內股份亦普遍跟隨油價回吐，細價股山東墨龍(00568)A股(002490.SZ)跌4.4%，報6.08元。中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)也跌4.06%，報8.51元；中海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)跌0.84%，報25.94元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15140247-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%8e%a2%e5%ba%95-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c13%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c0-17-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-01 15:10:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
